 Kidnapped mini campaign

 Overview:
 The player finds out about human trafficking and save a group of children and gets then drawn into other missions that try to engage the human traffickers.

 Missions:

 Kidnapped:
 The player is contaced by a couple that states their children were taken from them. He is asked to eavesdrop on some pirates and then rescue the children.
 Type: Board and return

 The Ruse:
 Player is asked to reunite a woman with her brother, after boarding he needs to puruse a ship or flee the system.
 Type: Board and flee

